    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i just feel like i've been doing everything right lately. my diet is super clean and i'm exercising way more than before. wouldnt that naturally thin my blood a bit more anyway? it just seems like such a high dose to stay on forever if my stats are actually improving. i just want to know if 2mg is a reasonable maintenance amount to aim for.",
